  "slug": "roundup-55",
  "html": "<p><em>GM Regens! ğŸ‘‹</em></p><p><em><a href=\"https://www.gaoa.work/\">Gabriel</a> here, a knowledge worker focused on high-impact research to help <a href=\"https://twitter.com/GAOAframework/status/1633737521183219713?s=20\">self-managed</a> individuals (DAOists) and organizations (DAOs) achieve efficient collaboration, enhanced productivity, effective decision-making and clarity of purpose. I'm experimenting in the intersection of Web3, Cognitive Science and the Creator Economy with the vision of fostering the <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/groups/14157407/\">future of work</a> and <a href=\"https://linktr.ee/gaoanetwork\">Integral Education</a>.</em></p><p><em>In this week's edition, we'll be diving into the human component of ReFi: individual level of coherence and our collective capacity for coordination, <em>and as always, we'll be sharing top news, events, and jobs from the ReFi world and beyond. Let's jump right in. </em></em>ğŸ‘‡</p><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/03/image-15.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/03/image-15.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/03/image-15.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/03/image-15.png 1280w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px\"><figcaption>with Midjourney.</figcaption></figure><h1 id=\"playing-the-infinite-game-of-refi-%E2%99%BE%EF%B8%8F\">Playing the Infinite Game of ReFi â™¾ï¸</h1><p><em>According to the renowned game theorist, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com.au/Finite-Infinite-Games-James-Carse/dp/1476731713\">James Carse</a>, there are at least two kinds of games. One could be called finite, the other infinite. A finite game is played for the purpose of winning, <strong>while an infinite game is for the purpose of continuing the play</strong>.</em></p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gaoa97/status/1633650793638395906?s=20\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">ReFi is an infinite game</a> energized by the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/owocki/status/1443567700198842373?s=20\">solarpunk</a> and <a href=\"https://mycopunks.gitbook.io/mycopunk-principles/\">mycopunk</a> movements, with a shared culture based on <strong>co-creation</strong> and <strong>cross-pollination</strong>, a collective awareness of the current economic system failures: unsustainability and unfairness, and a common willingness to rethink and redesign society from a systemic level. </p><p>But where do we start? ğŸ¤”</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">10/ <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> is the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/integral?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#integral</a> use of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/DeFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#DeFi</a> to play the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/infinite?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#infinite</a> game of regeneration.<a href=\"https://t.co/w8DKxwF3DX\">https://t.co/w8DKxwF3DX</a></p>&mdash; gaoa.eth (@gaoa97) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gaoa97/status/1633650793638395906?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 9, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"individual-coherence-collective-coordination-lasting-impact-%F0%9F%92%A5\">Individual coherence + collective coordination = lasting Impact ğŸ’¥</h3><p><em>It's easy to think of ourselves as separate from the earth, just temporary inhabitants passing through. But what if we viewed <strong>ourselves as an integral part of the planet</strong>, connected inextricably to every living thing around us?</em></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a href=\"https://plumvillage.org/podcast/from-extraction-to-regeneration-healing-ourselves-healing-society-episode-16/\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/03/Group-122.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1134\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/03/Group-122.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/03/Group-122.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/03/Group-122.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w2400/2023/03/Group-122.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a><figcaption>Thich Nhat Hanh, Buddhist Monk, and author</figcaption></figure><p>This is the idea behind higher levels of consciousness described by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheKenWilber\">Ken Wilber</a> on <a href=\"https://gaoa.notion.site/A-Theory-of-Everything-An-Integral-Vision-for-Business-Politics-Science-and-Spirituality-by-Ken--d084fe3323ba40e98d7d86a21035ee82\">Integral Theory</a>, the concept that as we transcend through ego developmental stages, we begin to see ourselves not as separate individuals but <strong>as part of a larger whole</strong>. </p><p>We move from being ego-centric to ethno-centric to world centric, and eventually, we arrive at a kosmo-centric state of mind, where we see the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gaoa97/status/1541933080575082496?s=20\">interconnectedness </a>of all things. As seen in the illustration below ğŸ‘‡ğŸ½</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card kg-card-hascaption\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"ca\" dir=\"ltr\">AQAL Integral Map <a href=\"https://t.co/WvpYMbWKGM\">pic.twitter.com/WvpYMbWKGM</a></p>&mdash; âšª GAOAğšğš›ğšŠğš–ğšğš ğš˜ğš›ğš” (@GAOAframework) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/GAOAframework/status/1628677164781666304?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 23, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n<figcaption>All Quadrants. All Levels - Ken Wilber</figcaption></figure><blockquote><em>We are nature. </em><br><em>We are the system. </em><br><em>The system is part of a bigger system...</em></blockquote><h2 id=\"bridging-the-gap-between-humanity-and-nature%F0%9F%8D%83\">Bridging the Gap Between Humanity and NatureğŸƒ Â </h2><p>In essence, to truly regenerate the planet, we must first undergo a <strong>paradigm shift within ourselves</strong>. This includes elevating our state of consciousness and embracing Â <a href=\"https://gaoa.notion.site/The-future-of-management-is-teal-ff9d8b3ae45a4f3485b9eee0c216837f\">Teal organizational structures</a>: principles of self-management, decentralized decision-making, and <a href=\"https://norabateson.wordpress.com/2015/11/03/symmathesy-a-word-in-progress/\">living systems</a> that focus on a holistic, real-world impact and <strong>systemic transformation</strong>. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/03/image-19.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/03/image-19.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/03/image-19.png 980w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Teal organization illustration. Source: <a href=\"https://quantumleaders.com/the-living-organization-and-teal/\">Quantum Leaders</a></figcaption></figure><p>By prioritizing regenerative practices and leveraging the power of web3 infrastructure, we are able to go one step further and operate as a Decentralised Autonomous Regenerative Entity/Ecosystem (<a href=\"https://twitter.com/GAOAnetwork/status/1634023710721183744?s=20\">DARE</a>)â€”a term coined by one of ReFiâ€™s founding fathers <a href=\"https://capitalinstitute.org/\">John Fullerton</a>. As a result we can drive a transition towards a more sustainable and equitable future for both humanity and the planet.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.notion.so/gaoa/Regenerative-Capitalism-04-20-15-Final-pdf-806e2dbd9fac403996e7ec4d8e494f11\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read Jon Fullerton&#x27;s  paper</a></div><p><strong>LFGâ€”<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gaoanetwork/status/1633639382937907201?s=61&amp;t=0VW3BcOH3dE52IJjyGgjYQ\">Let's Flourishingly Grow</a> ğŸŒ±ğŸš€</strong></p><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"ecosystem-updates-%F0%9F%91%80\">Ecosystem Updates ğŸ‘€</h2></div><h2 id=\"in-sync-collaboration-on-chain-verification-%F0%9F%A4%9D\">In-sync collaboration + On-chain verification ğŸ¤</h2><p>In a world of zoom calls and remote working, nothing beats a real-life scene.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">This is why <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiDAOist?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ReFiDAOist</a>â€™s first step to decentralization and going to market is through local ReFi DAO nodesâ€¦ <br><br>In-person communities gathering to take climate action TOGETHER with publicly verifiable impact for all to see. <br><br>Coming to a startup city near you! <a href=\"https://t.co/z3dJlU00X0\">https://t.co/z3dJlU00X0</a></p>&mdash; jE â¤ï¸ Regeneration (@climateXcrypto) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto/status/1633545959002058752?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 8, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>And not just at ReFi DAO, other local regens communities are also popping up...</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/schellingpoint_?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@schellingpoint_</a> i learned that local greenpill/regen crypto chapters are starting ğŸŒ±ğŸ—º<br><br>the first are in china + in india. ğŸ‡¨ğŸ‡³ğŸ‡®ğŸ‡³ <br><br>if you want to start one in your city pls fill out this form: <a href=\"https://t.co/TqNGpF1PXM\">https://t.co/TqNGpF1PXM</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/wQVN73xZjw\">pic.twitter.com/wQVN73xZjw</a></p>&mdash; Owocki.Îth (ğŸ¤–,ğŸ’š) (@owocki) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/owocki/status/1632864125020934145?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 6, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>The goal is to integrate local nodes with <strong>individual coherence</strong> and capacity for <strong>collective coordination</strong>...</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Now, we are bringing all of these pieces together to create a global network rooted in local startup communities taking collective action â€”a nation in the cloud that gathers in person around a shared vision of regeneration.<br><br>Join us --&gt; <a href=\"https://t.co/eV8Yufz5iE\">https://t.co/eV8Yufz5iE</a> ğŸ’š<br><br>/7 <a href=\"https://t.co/8oWb2ipNLO\">pic.twitter.com/8oWb2ipNLO</a></p>&mdash; Monty Merlin Bryant ğŸ§™âœ¨ (@MontyMerlin) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MontyMerlin/status/1633105280006225920?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 7, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>What once sounded like science fiction has now become a reality with the <strong>emergence of Web3</strong>â€”a new era where digital connections and collaborations are redefining the way we play the infinite game of regeneration.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"und\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NetworkState?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NetworkState</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thenetworkstate?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@thenetworkstate</a> by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/balajis?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@balajis</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/ycBUZF6dE7\">https://t.co/ycBUZF6dE7</a></p>&mdash; gaoa.eth (@gaoa97) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gaoa97/status/1634010933403213829?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 10, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"how-might-better-futures-emerge\">How might better futures emerge?</h2><p>The <a href=\"https://radardao.xyz/\">RADAR</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Radarxyz/status/1626320472433467392?s=20\">community</a> has just released a new whitepaper proposing a theory of change as an approach to accelerating <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gaoa97/status/1626333165932642304?s=20\">better futures</a> through <strong>incentive-aligned coordination structures for lasting impact</strong>â€”creating positive-sum, self-sustaining ecosystems that support community and resist extraction.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">RADAR asks the question, how might better futures emerge? <br><br>Multiplayer Futures: Toward An Emergence Economy is our response. A not-so-litepaper, if you will.<br><br>We hope youâ€™ll join us:<a href=\"https://t.co/jx06ZuqVRc\">https://t.co/jx06ZuqVRc</a></p>&mdash; RADAR (@Radarxyz) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Radarxyz/status/1631030274631892995?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 1, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"how-can-we-improve-coordination\">How can we improve coordination?</h2><p><a href=\"https://t.co/A8MiPaTOqo\">Hypha</a>â€™s organisation-in-a-box technology not only enables decentralized entities to cross-pollinate, but also mobilize quickly and cheaply, with entirely configurable modules enabling token creation and customizable approaches that have already been deployed to multiple <a href=\"https://twitter.com/GAOAnetwork/status/1634023710721183744?s=20\">DAREs</a> as part of the alpha launch with <strong>waiting list now open for Beta launch</strong>. If youâ€™re interested in trialling Hyphaâ€™s regenerative technology for your DAO or your Ecosystem, reach out now to <a href=\"https://www.cognitoforms.com/Hypha1/hyphadaobetaprogrameoi\">register your interest</a>.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uwGaJJYiIcw?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"An introduction to Hypha\"></iframe></figure><h2 id=\"how-to-participate-in-coordination\">How to participate in coordination?</h2><p>The future of work is increasingly decentralized and online, yet many people don't have access to desktop computers. Helping to address this problem, <a href=\"https://amadao.io/\">amaDAO</a> is launching a mobile-firstâ€”<a href=\"https://blog.celo.org/a-carbon-negative-blockchain-its-here-and-it-s-celo-60228de36490\">developed on celo</a>â€”social network for DAOs <strong>that makes governance enjoyable and rewarding</strong>. <a href=\"https://linktr.ee/cakerydao\">Cakery</a> helps DAO members keep track of contributions and build an on-chain portfolio of skills, work and equity across decentralized projects.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Built on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Celo?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Celo</a> so any <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/DAO?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#DAO</a> can be carbon negative.<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a></p>&mdash; Cakery DAO (@CakeryDAO) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CakeryDAO/status/1635202582250659841?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 13, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"how-to-start-a-startup-society\">How to start a startup society?</h2><p><a href=\"https://jur.io/\">Jur</a> is building an application specific L1 to facilitate <strong>rapid experimentation of different governance, voting, coordination</strong> styles to serve online communities that could one day be significant enough to become a <a href=\"https://thenetworkstate.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Network State</a>.</p><p>Jur recently launched <a href=\"https://jur.io/society-awards/\">The Startup Society Foundersâ€™ Awards</a>. Invitations are open to join other like-minded builders to pitch your vision of your very own Startup Society.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uEiGF47tF_A?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"Startup Society Demo - How to build a web3 society?\"></iframe></figure><h2 id=\"supermodular-venture-studio-%F0%9F%91%80\">Supermodular Venture Studio! ğŸ‘€</h2><p>Open Source Software is another infinite game of collective intelligence, driven by a passion for continuous improvement and a shared belief that <strong>knowledge belongs to all of us</strong>. </p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gitcoin?s=20\">Gitcoin</a> believes in the potential of digital public goods to transform our world for the better and is working to unlock that potential by supporting and incentivizing developers to keep the game going.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://community.supermodular.xyz/t/why-gitcoin-could-substantially-impact-the-status-quo/92\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Why Gitcoin Could Substantially Impact the Status Quo</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">This piece was written as part of my